<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-GB">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Unifying Operations for RMLFS: A Single Platform Proposal</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A tailored proposal for RMLFS outlining the business case and ROI for consolidating Swiftcase, Monday.com, and disparate apps into the BigChange platform.">
    <meta name="author" content="Serge Fagelman, BigChange">
    
    <!-- SEO & Social Sharing -->
    <meta property="og:title" content="BigChange & RMLFS: Streamlining Success">
    <meta property="og:description" content="An interactive proposal exploring the benefits of replacing 7+ legacy systems with one powerful, all-in-one job management solution.">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://i.postimg.cc/9QYhwmgK/Big-Change-Logo1.png">
    
    <!-- JSON-LD for SoftwareApplication -->
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
      "name": "BigChange Job Management Platform",
      "applicationCategory": "BusinessApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "Web, iOS, Android",
      "offers": {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "price": "79.95",
        "priceCurrency": "GBP",
        "description": "Per user per month, includes software, tracking hardware, and support."
      },
      "provider": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "BigChange"
      }
    }
    </script>

    <!-- Inline CSS for Single-File Deployment -->
    <style>
        /* CSS Reset & Base Styles */
        :root {
            /* Brand Colors from BigChange Brand Guidelines */
            --bc-energy-blue: #0072CE;
            --bc-navy: #0A2240;
            --bc-green: #28E289;
            --bc-orange: #FF6B00;
            --bc-light-grey: #F4F4F4;
            --bc-charcoal: #282922;
            --bc-white: #FFFFFF;
            
            /* Spacing & Sizing Tokens */
            --spacing-1: 0.25rem;
            --spacing-2: 0.5rem;
            --spacing-4: 1rem;
            --spacing-6: 1.5rem;
            --spacing-8: 2rem;
            --spacing-12: 3rem;
            --spacing-16: 4rem;
            
            /* Other Design Tokens */
            --border-radius: 0.75rem;
            --box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --transition-speed: 0.3s;
        }

        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            color: var(--bc-charcoal);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
        }
        
        /* General Layout & Typography */
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--spacing-6); }
        section { padding: var(--spacing-16) 0; }
        h1, h2, h3, h4 { color: var(--bc-navy); line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
        h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        h2 { font-size: 2rem; }
        h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
        a { color: var(--bc-energy-blue); text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .section-title { text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-12); }
        .section-title .icon {
            color: var(--bc-energy-blue);
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            margin: 0 auto var(--spacing-4);
        }
        .chip {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: var(--spacing-1) var(--spacing-2);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            background-color: var(--bc-light-grey);
            color: var(--bc-navy);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        #hero {
            background-color: var(--bc-navy);
            color: var(--bc-white);
            padding-top: var(--spacing-16);
            padding-bottom: var(--spacing-16);
            text-align: center;
        }
        #hero h1, #hero h2, #hero p { color: var(--bc-white); }
        #hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
        #hero .subhead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 800px; margin: var(--spacing-4) auto var(--spacing-8); opacity: 0.9; }
        .cta-buttons { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: var(--spacing-4); flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all var(--transition-speed);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .btn-primary { background-color: var(--bc-energy-blue); color: var(--bc-white); }
        .btn-primary:hover { background-color: #005bb5; }
        .btn-secondary { background-color: transparent; color: var(--bc-white); border-color: var(--bc-white); }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background-color: var(--bc-white); color: var(--bc-navy); }
        
        /* Current -> Future Section */
        .infographic-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--spacing-12); align-items: start; }
        .state-card { background-color: var(--bc-light-grey); padding: var(--spacing-8); border-radius: var(--border-radius); }
        .state-card h3 { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-4); }
        .state-card ul { list-style: none; margin-top: var(--spacing-6); }
        .state-card li { padding-left: 2rem; position: relative; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4); }
        .state-card li::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            top: 5px;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .state-card.current li::before { background-color: var(--bc-orange); }
        .state-card.future li::before { background-color: var(--bc-green); }

        /* Business Case Section */
        .meddic-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-6); }
        .meddic-card { background-color: var(--bc-light-grey); padding: var(--spacing-6); border-radius: var(--border-radius); }
        .meddic-card h4 { color: var(--bc-energy-blue); font-size: 1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2); }
        .meddic-card h4 .icon { width: 20px; height: 20px; }
        .meddic-card p, .meddic-card ul { font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .meddic-card ul { list-style-position: inside; padding-left: var(--spacing-2); }
        .assumption-flag { color: var(--bc-orange); font-style: italic; font-size: 0.8rem; }
        .gantt-mini { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-2); }
        .gantt-mini-item { background-color: var(--bc-white); padding: var(--spacing-2) var(--spacing-4); border-radius: 0.5rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .gantt-mini-item > .chip {
            padding: var(--spacing-1) var(--spacing-4);
            line-height: 1.5;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        /* ROI Calculator Section */
        #roi { background-color: var(--bc-light-grey); }
        .calculator-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
            gap: var(--spacing-8);
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            padding: var(--spacing-8);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
        }
        .calculator-input { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-6); }
        .calculator-input label { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2); }
        .calculator-input label span:last-child { color: var(--bc-energy-blue); }
        input[type="range"] { -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none; width: 100%; height: 8px; background: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 5px; outline: none; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
        input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb { -webkit-appearance: none; appearance: none; width: 20px; height: 20px; background: var(--bc-energy-blue); cursor: pointer; border-radius: 50%; }
        .roi-results { text-align: center; }
        .total-savings { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--bc-green); line-height: 1; }
        #assumptions-container {
            margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            padding: var(--spacing-6);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
        }
        #assumptions-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: var(--spacing-4);
        }
        #assumptions-list p { font-size: 0.85rem; }

        /* SVG Donut Chart */
        .donut-chart-container { position: relative; width: 250px; height: 250px; margin: var(--spacing-6) auto; }
        .donut-chart { transform: rotate(-90deg); border-radius: 50%; }
        .donut-segment { fill: none; stroke-width: 20; transition: stroke-dashoffset 0.5s ease-in-out; }
        .donut-legend { list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: var(--spacing-6); flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: var(--spacing-4); }
        .donut-legend li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2); font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .legend-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
        
        .calculation-breakdown { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-4); }
        
        /* Other Sections */
        .gantt-chart { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--spacing-4); }
        .gantt-phase { background-color: var(--bc-white); padding: var(--spacing-4); border-radius: var(--border-radius); box-shadow: var(--box-shadow); }
        .gantt-phase h4 { margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2); display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--spacing-2); }
        .gantt-phase .icon { width: 24px; height: 24px; color: var(--bc-energy-blue); }
        .gantt-timeline { position: relative; height: 20px; background-color: #e0e0e0; border-radius: 10px; margin-top: var(--spacing-2); }
        .gantt-bar { position: absolute; height: 100%; background-color: var(--bc-energy-blue); border-radius: 10px; }

        /* New Detailed GANTT Chart Styles */
        .gantt-chart-detailed {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px repeat(12, 1fr); /* 1 label column, 12 week columns */
            gap: 5px;
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            padding: var(--spacing-4);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
        }
        .gantt-header {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--bc-light-grey);
        }
        .gantt-header-label { text-align: left; }
        .gantt-row {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 200px repeat(12, 1fr);
            gap: 5px;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bc-light-grey);
            padding: var(--spacing-2) 0;
            min-height: 60px;
        }
        .gantt-row-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding-right: var(--spacing-2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: var(--spacing-2);
        }
        .gantt-row-label .icon {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            color: var(--bc-energy-blue);
        }
        .gantt-bar-task {
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            background-color: var(--bc-energy-blue);
            color: var(--bc-white);
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: var(--spacing-1) var(--spacing-2);
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            transition: opacity var(--transition-speed);
        }
        .gantt-bar-task:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="kickoff"] { grid-column: 3 / 5; background-color: var(--bc-navy); } /* Adjusted to start after LMS */
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="core-config"] { grid-column: 4 / 7; background-color: var(--bc-energy-blue); }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="data-export"] { grid-column: 4 / 5; background-color: #0094d4; }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="data-import"] { grid-column: 5 / 7; background-color: #0094d4; }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="ppm-build"] { grid-column: 5 / 8; background-color: var(--bc-orange); }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="service-training"] { grid-column: 7 / 9; background-color: var(--bc-orange); }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="project-costing"] { grid-column: 6 / 9; background-color: #ff8c42; }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="xero-integration"] { grid-column: 8 / 10; background-color: #ff8c42; }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="finance-training"] { grid-column: 9 / 11; background-color: #ff8c42; }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="power-bi"] { grid-column: 10 / 13; background-color: var(--bc-green); }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="floorwalking"] { grid-column: 11 / 13; background-color: #22c55e; } /* Assuming go-live around week 10/11 */
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="review"] { grid-column: 13 / 14; background-color: var(--bc-navy); }
        .gantt-bar-task[data-task-id="lms-access"] { grid-column: 2 / 14; background-color: var(--bc-light-grey); color: var(--bc-charcoal); border: 1px dashed var(--bc-energy-blue); } /* Spans all weeks */
        
        /* Project Governance Table */
        .governance-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-6);
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .governance-table th, .governance-table td {
            border: 1px solid var(--bc-light-grey);
            padding: var(--spacing-4);
            text-align: left;
        }
        .governance-table th {
            background-color: var(--bc-light-grey);
            color: var(--bc-navy);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .governance-table td {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        .governance-table td strong {
            color: var(--bc-charcoal);
        }

        /* GANTT Modal Styles */
        .gantt-modal-overlay {
            display: none; /* Hidden by default */
            position: fixed; /* Stay in place */
            z-index: 1000; /* Sit on top */
            left: 0;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%; /* Full width */
            height: 100%; /* Full height */
            overflow: auto; /* Enable scroll if needed */
            background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6); /* Black w/ opacity */
            padding-top: 60px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.3s;
        }
        .gantt-modal-content {
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            margin: 5% auto;
            padding: var(--spacing-8);
            border: 1px solid #888;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 700px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
            animation: slideIn 0.3s;
        }
        .gantt-modal-close {
            color: #aaa;
            float: right;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            top: var(--spacing-4);
            right: var(--spacing-6);
        }
        .gantt-modal-close:hover,
        .gantt-modal-close:focus {
            color: var(--bc-charcoal);
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #gantt-modal-body ul {
            list-style: disc;
            list-style-position: inside;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-4);
        }
        #gantt-modal-body li {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2);
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        @keyframes slideIn {
            from { transform: translateY(-50px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; }
        }
        
        /* Proposal Section */
        #proposal {
            background-color: var(--bc-light-grey);
        }
        .proposal-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: var(--spacing-8);
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
        }
        .proposal-card {
            background-color: var(--bc-white);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            padding: var(--spacing-8);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
            border: 3px solid transparent;
            text-align: center;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        .proposal-card.deal {
            border-color: var(--bc-energy-blue);
            transform: scale(1.05);
            position: relative;
        }
        .proposal-card-deal-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background-color: var(--bc-energy-blue);
            color: var(--bc-white);
            padding: var(--spacing-1) var(--spacing-4);
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .proposal-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: var(--bc-navy);
        }
        .proposal-card .price {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--bc-navy);
            margin: var(--spacing-4) 0;
        }
        .proposal-card .price-rrp {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #777;
            text-decoration: line-through;
            margin: var(--spacing-4) 0;
        }
        .proposal-card p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .cta-center {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: var(--spacing-8);
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .proposal-wrapper {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }

        /* End New Styles */

        /* Footer */
        footer { background-color: var(--bc-navy); color: var(--bc-light-grey); padding: var(--spacing-8) 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        #sources { margin-top: var(--spacing-4); }
        #sources ul { list-style: none; }
        
        /* Responsive Styles */
        @media (max-width: 1024px) {
            .infographic-grid, .calculator-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
            #hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            section { padding: var(--spacing-12) 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <section id="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                    <div style="padding: 10px;">
                        <img src="https://rmlfs.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/RML-logo-white.svg" alt="RMLFS Logo" style="height: 65px;">
                    </div>
                    <span style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--bc-energy-blue);">+</span>
                    <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/ydbgqXFm/Big-Change-White.png" alt="BigChange Logo" style="height: 54px;">
                </div>
                <h1>Consolidating 7+ Systems into One Powerful Platform for RMLFS</h1>
                <p class="subhead">A strategic proposal to eliminate app fatigue and data silos. Move from Swiftcase, Monday.com, AssetGo, and manual spreadsheets to a single, unified solution that scales with your ambition.</p>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="https://app.fireflies.ai/view/BigChange-x-RMLFS-Ltd::01KAG7ZTQT2R066TPWFCAZCPHC" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color: var(--bc-orange);">Watch Demo Recording</a>
                    <a href="#roi" class="btn btn-primary">Calculate ROI & Savings</a>
                    <a href="#investment" class="btn btn-secondary">View Investment</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="current-future">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-title">
                     <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.813 15.904L9 18.75l-.813-2.846a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09-3.09L2.25 12l2.846-.813a4.5 4.5 0 003.09-3.09L9 5.25l.813 2.846a4.5 4.5 0 003.09 3.09L15.75 12l-2.846.813a4.5 4.5 0 00-3.09 3.09zM18.259 8.715L18 9.75l-.259-1.035a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.455-2.456L14.25 6l1.036-.259a3.375 3.375 0 002.455-2.456L18 2.25l.259 1.035a3.375 3.375 0 002.456 2.456L21.75 6l-1.035.259a3.375 3.375 0 00-2.456 2.456zM16.898 20.562L16.25 22.5l-.648-1.938a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.473-1.473L12 18.75l1.938-.648a2.25 2.25 0 011.473-1.473L16.25 15l.648 1.938a2.25 2.25 0 011.473 1.473L20.25 18.75l-1.938.648a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.473 1.473z" /></svg>
                    <h2>Current State vs. Future State</h2>
                    <p>Transforming RMLFS from a complex web of disconnected apps to a streamlined, automated operation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="infographic-grid">
                    <div class="state-card current">
                        <h3>
                             <!-- Generic icon for disjointed systems -->
                             <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#FF6B00" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="margin-right: 10px;"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"></path><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"></path></svg>
                            Current State (System Overload)
                        </h3>
                        <ul>
                            <li><strong>Too Many Systems:</strong> Juggling Swiftcase, Monday.com, AssetGo, iAuditor, Quartix, Connect Team, and Excel is inefficient and costly.</li>
                            <li><strong>Manual Planning:</strong> Scheduling is still done on spreadsheets outside of the main system, creating double entry and confusion.</li>
                            <li><strong>Lack of Visibility:</strong> Cannot easily see who is nearest to a job or track time on site accurately.</li>
                            <li><strong>Reporting Gaps:</strong> Swiftcase dashboards aren't delivering the real-time project and financial data needed for decision-making.</li>
                            <li><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Admitted struggle to keep up with client updates as the business grows.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
